## 3. API Source

### JSONPlaceholder API

API endpoint used:

https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users

### Purpose

JSONPlaceholder was used as a test API source to practice API data retrieval.

The `/users` endpoint provides sample user data in JSON format, including information such as:

- User ID
- Name
- Username
- Email
- Address
- Phone number
- Website
- Company information

### Relevance to the Project

This API was useful to practice:

- API requests
- JSON data extraction
- Data normalization
- Transforming nested JSON into tabular format
- Working with user-related information

Although the API is a fake test API, it was useful for practicing data retrieval and data wrangling techniques.

